# Local code-review tool exports — not for git.
# CSV exports from review bots (Codeball, Qodana, Copilot Review, etc.)
# are noise: priority/category are usually wrong, comment bodies are
# missing, and they're regenerated on every review run. Keep locally
# for one-shot triage, then delete.
